channel.title: I was lucky to see it (Engine Error)
channel.description:
This one comes out on a level where first trampolins appear. When i killed that big fire-shooting-robot, i let his hand jump on trampolins and then i saw this.
![](upload://xjPTlSKgjPYfp023eW7oKobtbZA.jpeg)
Actually, that's not a problem. Just want to let the DevTeam know. Just love you guys :slight_smile:
